             was indicted for <rs id="t18070218-46-off253" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070218-46-off253" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070218-46-off253" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               that he about the hour of twelve at night, on the <rs id="t18070218-46-cd254" type="crimeDate">10th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070218-46-off253 t18070218-46-cd254"></join>, being in the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18070218-46-victim485" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Dawson
                        <interp inst="t18070218-46-victim485" type="surname" value="Dawson"></interp>
