                  , feloniously did steal a trunk, value 5 s. a sheet, value 1 s. two petticoats, value 2 s. two gowns, value 2 s. a pair of shoes, value 6 d. a table cloth, value 6 d. and a sheet, value 1 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18070218-46-person486">
                        Thomas 
                        Dawson
                     <interp inst="t18070218-46-person486" type="surname" value="Dawson"></interp>
